// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1381 — Mass File Rename (play)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3cdf0ac9-476b-5e71-9277-15869a412995

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
